<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="a5Aug1940"><font color="red">5 August 1940</font> <i>Letters III</i> (to Jacques Mercanton): I should like to move [Lucia] &mdash; with the permission of the German, French and Swiss authorities &mdash; to your country and even to go with her. I have written to this effect to the Swiss Legation at Lyons, quai du General Sanais. Up to now I have had no reply. </div>
